> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Concept:** 1 Card = 1 Team (containing multiple agents).
> - **Colors:** Use App Primary `#55b7e0` (Blue/Cyan) and Grey/Slate tones. **No Green/Amber**.
> - **Badges:** Active = Primary Color. Pending = Grey. Approved = Primary.

