## Proposed Changes

### 1. Rename & Refactor

#### [RENAME] [AgentBuilder.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Daniel%20Roldan%20CT/Desktop/Innagent%20%20CustomerAGI%20Proyect/Innagent/pages/AgentBuilder.tsx) → `AgentEditor.tsx`
The existing editor becomes the sub-page for configuring a specific agent.

#### [NEW] `pages/AITeamGallery.tsx`
The new landing page for `/agents`.

**Layout & Design:**
- **Header:** "AI Team" title + "Create Team" button (or similar global action).
- **Grid:** Responsive grid of **Team Cards**.
- **Card Design:**
  - Dark background (`bg-[#161b2e]`).
  - **Top Section:**
    - **Icon:** Rounded customizable icon (Trophy, Cash, Handshake, Gear, etc.).
    - **Team Name:** H3 Bold.
  - **Middle Section:**
    - **"Agents Inside":** List of agents in the team.
    - Each item in the list is clickable -> navigates to `AgentEditor` for that agent.
  - **Bottom Actions (Side-by-Side):**
    - **Primary Button:** "Create Agent" (Goes to blank Agent Form for this team).
    - **Secondary Button:** "Configure Team" (Goes to Team Settings - placeholder for now, maybe `AgentEditor` default per instruction).

### 2. Feature Enhancements (AgentEditor)

**Header:**
- Add **"Duplicate into a Team"** dropdown button.
- Update "Save Draft" / "Publish" to show **Status Badges** on click.
  - **Saved/Active:** Primary Blue Pill (`#55b7e0`).
  - **Unsaved/Pending:** Grey Pill.

**Content:**
- **Custom Tone:** Add "Custom" pill. When selected, show a text input below.
- **Chat Preview:** "Send" button triggers a "No AI Connected yet" popup.

### 3. Routing & Navigation

#### [MODIFY] [App.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Daniel%20Roldan%20CT/Desktop/Innagent%20%20CustomerAGI%20Proyect/Innagent/App.tsx)
- Route `/agents` → `AITeamGallery`
- Route `/agents/new` → `AgentEditor` (blank state)
- Route `/agents/:id` → `AgentEditor` (with ID)

#### [MODIFY] [Sidebar.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Daniel%20Roldan%20CT/Desktop/Innagent%20%20CustomerAGI%20Proyect/Innagent/components/Sidebar.tsx)
- Rename label: "Agents" → "AI Team"

